    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要把SmartEdify的Outbox流程可视化一下，核心是展示从领域事务提交到最终Kafka投递的完整链路。先画一个Domain TX的子图，里面包含Domain Aggregate Change、Persist Aggregate和Insert Outbox Row JSON这三个步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain TX",
        "Domain Aggregate Change",
        "Persist Aggregate",
        "Insert Outbox Row JSON"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这三个都在同一个事务边界内。那事务提交节点TX Commit是放在子图内部还是外部？从语义上看，Commit应该是子图的出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TX Commit",
        "Domain TX"
