    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TX Commit放在子图外面，作为整个事务的终点。然后用虚线箭头把A、B、C串起来指向D，标注Commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "Commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图和事务提交流程已画好。接下来是Outbox Poller的部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Outbox Poller / Publisher Loader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Poller作为独立节点E，从TX Commit之后开始。然后需要Deserialize + Envelope Enrichment，这是F节点。注意这里不是直接发Kafka，要先做数据转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "Deserialize",
        "Envelope Enrichment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Deserialize具体指什么？是解析Outbox Row里的JSON吗？",
